-star-tells-of-coke-and-booze-orgy-with-charlie-sheen-before-hospital-dash-115875-22882934/ |title=The Mirror |publisher=The Mirror |date=2011-01-29 |accessdate=2011-02-21}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=Cl1OAAAAIBAJ&sjid=9_wDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4869,6687172&dq=charlie-sheen+donna&hl=en |title=Lakeland Ledger \u2013 February 20, 1996 |date=1996-02-20 |accessdate=2011-02-21}}</ref><ref name=\"nineteen\" />\n|-\n|[[Irving Berlin]] and Dorothy Goetz\n|5 months\n|February 1912 \u2014 July 17, 1912\n|Unlike most listed here, the end of the marriage was caused by Goetz contracting [[typhoid fever]] on their Cuban honeymoon and dying. Berlin's second marriage would last 62 years.\n|-\n|[[Drew Barrymore]] and [[Tom Green]]\n|163 days\n|July 7 \u2013 December 17, 2001\n|\n|<ref>{{cite web |last=Silverman |first=Stephen M. |url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,26334,622131,00.html |title=(magazine) |publisher=People |date=2001-07-10 |accessdate=2011-02-21 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080605161742/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,26334,622131,00.html |archivedate=2008-06-05 |df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Darst |first=Jeanne |url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,26334,623114,00.html |title=(magazine) |publisher=People |date=2001-12-18 |accessdate=2011-02-21 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081005070527/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,26334,623114,00.html |archivedate=2008-10-05 |df= }}</ref><ref name=\"nineteen\" />\n|-\n|[[Shannen Doherty]] and [[Ashley Hamilton]]\n|> 6 months\n|1993 \u2013 March 1994\n|\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=GcIdAAAAIBAJ&sjid=1r4EAAAAIBAJ&pg=6891,4601899&dq=ashley+hamilton&hl=en |title=Sarasota Herald-Tribune \u2013 April 8, 1994 |date= |accessdate=2011-02-21}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=CHMaAAAAIBAJ&sjid=zCwEAAAAIBAJ&pg=5321,6847621&dq=ashley+hamilton&hl=en |title=The Milwaukee Journal \u2013 April 7, 1994 |date= |accessdate=2011-02-21}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Kim Darby]] and [[James Stacy]]\n|7 months\n|\n|\n|<ref name=\"The Prescott Courier \u2013 Google News Archive Search\" />\n|-\n|[[Michael Jackson]] and [[Lisa Marie Presley]]\n|9 months\n|\n|\n|<ref name=\"nineteen\" />\n|-\n|[[Rick Salomon]] and [[Shannen Doherty]]\n|9 months\n|2002\u20132003\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Elizabeth Taylor]] and [[Conrad Hilton]]\n|205 days\n|May 6 \u2013 November 27, 1950\n|\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://content.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,2098279_2098285_2098304,00.html|title=Top 10 Short-Lived Celebrity Marriages|first=Erin|last=Skarda|date=November 1, 2011|via=content.time.com}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Jennifer Lopez]] and [[Cris Judd]]\n|218 days\n|September 2001 \u2013 June 2002\n|\n|<ref name=\"nineteen\" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://content.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,2098279_2098285_2098299,00.html|title=Top 10 Short-Lived Celebrity Marriages|first=Allison|last=Berry|date=November 1, 2011|via=content.time.com}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Jim Carrey]] and [[Lauren Holly]]\n|10 months\n|September 1996 \u2013 July 1997\n|\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=93hjAAAAIBAJ&sjid=dXkNAAAAIBAJ&pg=6744,2036281&dq=jim-carrey+holly&hl=en |title=The Madison Courier \u2013 July 30, 1997 |date= |accessdate=2011-02-21}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=7PAvAAAAIBAJ&sjid=w_wDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6726,5361284&dq=jim-carrey+holly&hl=en |title=Lakeland Ledger \u2013 August 27, 1997 |date=1997-08-27 |accessdate=2011-02-21}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Woody Harrelson]] and Nancy Simon\n|10 months\n|\n|Married in Tijuana with the intent of getting a [[Mexican divorce]] afterward. The divorce did not occur until ten months later as the \"divorce stand\" was closed.\n|<ref>[https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=c4YfAAAAIBAJ&sjid=nM4EAAAAIBAJ&pg=6511,1992896&dq=woody-harrelson+nancy&hl=en Herald-Journal \u2013 October 3, 1989]: \"It seemed li