l''\n| Elena\n| \n|\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''Stranded''\n| Julia\n|\n|\n|-\n|2019\n|''Mga Mata sa Dilim''\n|\n|\n|\n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist|2|refs=\n\n<ref name='Huming Ako Sa Langit trailer'>{{cite video | people= Mendiola, Jessy (Cast) | title= Humingi Ako Sa Langit Trailer | url= https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l5399o-Z1YY | language= Filipino | publisher= ABS-CBN |location= Philippines | access-date= December 20, 2010| time=1:25}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Reunion\">{{cite web | url = http://www.sunstar.com.ph/manila/entertainment/asap-rocks-reunites-big-names-showbiz | title = 'ASAP Rocks' reunites big names in showbiz | work = Entertainment | publisher = SunStar Manila | date = February 19, 2011 | access-date = April 12, 2011}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Showstopping Performance\">{{cite web | url = http://www.pep.ph/guide/tv/7956/asap-rocks-promises-showstopping-performances-this-sunday | title = ASAP Rocks promises showstopping performances this Sunday | work = Guide / Television | publisher = The Philippine Entertainment Portal | date = April 9, 2011 | access-date = April 12, 2011}}</ref>\n\n<ref name='Launching Project'>{{cite web | url = http://www.pep.ph/news/27593/Jessy-Mendiola-on-her-launching-soap,-Sabel:-Para-akong-lumulutang! | title = Jessy Mendiola on her launching soap, Sabel: \"Para akong lumulutang!\" | work = News | author = Llanera, Melba | publisher = The Philippine Entertainment Portal | date = December 6, 2010 | access-date = December 20, 2010}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Writer\">{{cite web|url=http://www.philstar.com/cebu-entertainment/2013/11/02/1252192/pokwang-returns-comedy-call-center-girl|title=Pokwang returns to comedy in ''Call Center Girl''|publisher=Philstar|access-date=November 2, 2013}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Gimik 2010\">{{cite web | url = http://www.pep.ph/guide/6005/%3Cem%3EGimik-2010-%3C/em%3Ebrings-together-Judy-Ann-Santos,-Diether-Ocampo,-Bojo-Molina,-G--Toengi,-and-Mylene-Dizon | archive-url = https://archive.today/20120907044108/http: