S-CBN |access-date=December 20, 2010 |date=March 28, 2010 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110724092833/http://telebisyon.net/balita/Jessie-Mendiola-prefers-to-take-it-slow-with-Coco-Martin/artikulo/99874/ |archive-date=July 24, 2011 |df= }}</ref>\n\n<ref name='Marriage Contract'>{{cite web | url = http://www.pep.ph/guide/6950/Xian-Lim-and-Jessy-Mendiolas-characters-get-married-in-MMK | title = Xian Lim and Jessy Mendiola's characters get \"married\" in MMK | work = Entertainment Guide/Television | author = Erece, Dino | publisher = The Philippine Entertainment Portal | date = October 6, 2010 | access-date = December 20, 2010 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101010131255/http://www.pep.ph/guide/6950/Xian-Lim-and-Jessy-Mendiolas-characters-get-married-in-MMK | archive-date = October 10, 2010 | url-status = dead }}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Jessy is Sabel\">{{cite web|last=Franco |first=Bernie |title=Jessy Mendiola is the lead star of new teleserye 'Sabel' |url=http://www.push.com.ph/news-feature/1346/Jessy-Mendiola-is-the-lead-star-of-new-teleserye-Sabel-.aspx |publisher=Push.com.ph |access-date=December 1, 2010 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101203020140/http://www.push.com.ph/news-feature/1346/Jessy-Mendiola-is-the-lead-star-of-new-teleserye-Sabel-.aspx |archive-date= December 3, 2010 |df= }}</ref>\n\n<ref name='Star Magic Batch 15'>{{cite web|url=http://telebisyon.net/balita/Star-Magic-Batch-15-Ready-for-their-closeups/artikulo/34250/ |work=Life & Entertainment |author=Isah V. Red |publisher=Manila Standard Today |title=Star Magic Batch 15: Ready for their close-ups |access-date=December 20, 2010 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110724092827/http://telebisyon.net/balita/Star-Magic-Batch-15-Ready-for-their-closeups/artikulo/34250/ |archive-date=July 24, 2011 |df= }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Sexiest Woman of the Philippines 2016\">{{cite news|url=http://news.abs-cbn.com/entertainmen