 Rachelle | date = April 16, 2011 | access-date = April 19, 2011 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110523090332/http://www.abs-cbn.com/Feature/Article/9553/On-Maalaala-Mo-Kaya-Jessy-Mendiola-and-Ejay-Falcon-pursue-bolder-roles.aspx | archive-date = May 23, 2011 | url-status = dead }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Journal\">{{cite web | url=http://www.journal.com.ph/index.php?issue=2007-07-27&sec=3&aid=25917 | title=Prettiest New Stars at ABS-CBN | access-date=June 1, 2008 | work=People's Journal | author=Bautista, Mario E | publisher=People's Journal | date=July 27, 2007}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Jessie Mendiola on the buzz\">{{cite web|url=http://www.philstar.com/index.php?Showbiz&p=50&type=2&sec=58&aid=2007060297 |title=Star Magic Batch 15 |access-date=July 15, 2008 |author=Miralles, Nitz |work=About Showbiz |publisher=The Philippine Star |date=June 3, 2007 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070909044807/http://www.philstar.com/index.php?Showbiz&p=50&type=2&sec=58&aid=2007060297 |archive-date=September 9, 2007 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Malaya\">{{cite web|url=http://www.malaya.com.ph/jul28/ente_2.htm |title=Polo launches dance group on rival network |access-date=July 15, 2008 |author=Bautista, Mario E. |work=Dream Factory |publisher=Malaya Entertainment |date=July 28, 2007 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080606194150/http://www.malaya.com.ph/jul28/ente_2.htm |archive-date= June 6, 2008 |df= }}</ref>\n\n<ref name='First details'>{{cite web | url=http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/entertainment/10/28/14/first-details-new-richard-dawn-serye | title=First details of new Richard-Dawn serye | publisher=ABS-CBN News | date=October 28, 2014 | accessdate=October 28, 2014}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"PHR: Paraiso\">{{cite web|url=http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/entertainment/04/24/12/matteo-jessy-jewel-star-new-series|title=Matteo, Jessy, Jewel to star in new series|accessdate=October 13, 2012}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Ang Probinsyano\">{{cite web | url = http://news.abs-cbn.com/entertainment/03/21/18/jessy-mendiola-added-to-cast-of-ang-probinsyano | title = Jessy Mendiola Added to Cast of 'Ang Probinsyano' | publisher = ABS-CBN News | date = March 21, 2018 | accessdate = March 21, 2018}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Sandugo\">{{cite web |last1=Anarcon |first1=James Patrick |title=Jessy Mendiola ends network transfer rumors through this project |url=https://www.pep.ph/guide/tv/144906/jessy-mendiola-ends-network-transfer-rumors-through-this-project-a724-20190729 | website=[[Philippine Entertainment Portal]] | date=July 29, 2019 | accessdate= September 6, 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Volta\">{{cite news | url = https://www.philstar.com/entertainment/2008/01/18/39266/ai-ai-ready-take-flight | title = Ai Ai Ready to Take Flight | author = Ra\u00f1oa-Bismarck, Maridol | date = January 18, 2008 | newspaper = [[The Philippine Star]] | accessdate = August 4, 2018}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"MMFF 2018\">{{cite web |last1=Guerrero |first1=Faye |title=Jericho defends Jessy against those questioning her inclusion in MMFF 2018 entry |url=https://www.pep.ph/guide/tv/28197/jericho-defends-jessy-against-those-questioning-her-inclusion-in-mmff-2018-entry | website=[[Philippine Entertainment Portal]] |date=July 17, 2018 |accessdate=October 18, 2018}}</ref>\n\n}}\n\n== External links ==\n* {{IMDb name|2686231}}\n* {{Twitter}}\n{{S-start}}\n{{succession box\n| before = [[Jennylyn Mercado]]\n| title = [[FHM Philippines|FHM Philippines<br />Sexiest Woman of the Year]]\n| years = '''(2016)'''\n| after = [[Nadine Lustre]]\n}}\n{{S-end}}\n\n{{Top spot in the FHM Philippines \"100 Sexiest Women\"}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Mendiola, Jessy}}\n[[Category:1992 births]]\n[[Category:Filipino child actresses]]\n[[Category:Filipino television actresses]]\n[[Category:Filipino people of British descent]]\n[[Category:Filipino people of Lebanese descent]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Star Magic Batch 15]]\n[[Category:Star Magic]